Package: cloudberry-backup
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, cloudberry (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Backup and restore utilities for Apache Cloudberry
 Cloudberry Backup packages the gpbackup, gprestore, gpbackup_helper,
 and gpbackup_s3_plugin utilities for Apache Cloudberry.
 .
 This package installs the backup tools into /usr/cloudberry/bin.
